<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Plans_for_more_atomic_attacks_on_Japan"><span class="tocnumber">6</span> <span class="toctext">Plans for more atomic attacks on Japan</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#The_surrender_of_Japan_and_subsequent_occupation"><span class="tocnumber">7</span> <span class="toctext">The surrender of Japan and subsequent occupation</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Atomic_Bomb_Casualty_Commission"><span class="tocnumber">8</span> <span class="toctext">Atomic Bomb Casualty Commission</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#The_hibakusha"><span class="tocnumber">9</span> <span class="toctext">The hibakusha</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Korean_survivors"><span class="tocnumber">9.1</span> <span class="toctext">Korean survivors</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Double_survivor"><span class="tocnumber">9.2</span> <span class="toctext">Double survivor</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Debate_over_bombings"><span class="tocnumber">10</span> <span class="toctext">Debate over bombings</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#See_also"><span class="tocnumber">11</span> <span class="toctext">See also</span></a></li>
