<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFOgura1948">Ogura, Toyofumi (1948). <i>Letters from the End of the World: A Firsthand Account of the Bombing of Hiroshima</i>. Kodansha International Ltd.. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/4770027761" class="internal">ISBN 4-7700-2776-1</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Letters+from+the+End+of+the+World%3A+A+Firsthand+Account+of+the+Bombing+of+Hiroshima&amp;rft.aulast=Ogura&amp;rft.aufirst=Toyofumi&amp;rft.au=Ogura%2C+Toyofumi&amp;rft.date=1948&amp;rft.pub=Kodansha+International+Ltd.&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Atomic_bombings_of_Hiroshima_and_Nagasaki"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
